title: BigFish - Coffee House Chaos - Dash Game - Requested [h33t][Wend
description:
Coffee House Chaos


Quickly brew up coffee for a variety of kooky customers 
in this deliciously blended puzzle and action game. 
Seat your patrons, take orders, and deliver their cups 
of coffee before the coffee house becomes too chaotic 
and they leave without paying. Upgrade your coffee shop 
and menu to make more profits and attract more customers.

    * 25 fast-paced levels.
    * 3 modes to choose from.
    * Classic game play.
System Requirements:
OS: Windows 2000/XP/VISTA
CPU: 600MHz or faster Processor
RAM: 128 MB
